26:10.889 --> 26:18.902
So, in principle, you can have some sort of free 
trade in the middle of the sea. Is this an idiotic

26:19.302 --> 26:20.424
idea? No. You don't think so? No. What about 
spillhouses, cities on the sea? I think that's all

26:27.918 --> 26:29.380
fun. And John Craven, too, of course, is working on 
